  "description": "Prismatic Sump Store serves as the residence’s sealed service chamber, where the grounded gutters converge before feeding the central lensing cistern. Facet-tiled walls and a ribbed slagglass ceiling impose the city’s calibrated twilight bands as hard color bars across stacked bins and numbered canisters. A shallow floor trough collects electrostatic glass dust into removable sediment trays, keeping the chamber’s contents free of charge bloom and abrasive grit. Fixed mirror-plates set into the inner doorframe record the auroral regimen as steady reference marks for inventory control.",
